4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week Data Science & Machine Learning course. The course is designed for beginners with no previous experience required. It covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and prepares students to become professional Data Analysts. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also includes real-life case studies and teaches students how to develop their own AI projects from development to deployment and maintenance. The course is taught in English or Spanish and includes three classes per week with a maximum class size of 12 students. Upon completion of the course, students receive a recognized certificate. More information can be found on the 4Geeks Academy website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop